    <title>Mystic Brew</title>
    <link>https://www.pbsfm.org.au/program/mystic-brew</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;Mystic Brew is a melting pot of soul, jazz, electronica, hip hop &amp;amp; everything else in-between from all over the world without barriers or borders, joining the dots between the past, present &amp;amp; future.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;General info/enquires: &lt;a href="mailto:mysticbrewpbs@gmail.com" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(204, 34, 41); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;" target="_blank"&gt;mysticbrewpbs@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Send your music to: &lt;a href="mailto:mysticbrewpromo@gmail.com" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(204, 34, 41); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;" target="_blank"&gt;mysticbrewpromo@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt; (Please note I now only accept digital downloads &amp;amp; vinyl.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For more info on Mike Gurrieri &amp;amp; DJ bookings head to &lt;a href="http://www.mikegurrieri.net/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(204, 34, 41); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;" target="_blank" title="www.mikegurrieri.net"&gt;www.mikegurrieri.net&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
